    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I know, I know... but sometimes the most loving thing you can do is step aside so others can live their own lives without looking over their shoulder worrying about you. If I were her, I'd want to be free of this responsibility. I just wonder if there's a way to just... make it stop. To just let go quietly so they can finally have their peace back. Do you think people ever realize that leaving might actually be the kindest thing they could do for those they love?",
